reviewText: Great gift for a little girl. The story line is good and clean.

my twins are a big fan of the original strawberry shortcake movies, and the only place i can get them is through amazon. they have a great selection and ordering from here was a satisfactory experience.

For as much use as my daughter (now 5) gets out of this collection, I'd have gladly paid twice what it cost. I am impressed with the production of the set, the quality materials (so many of these children's dvd sets just fall apart), an the re-watch potential. Five stars all the way around!
I have a 6 year old girl and a 4 year old boy and they just love Strawberry Shortcake. This is one collection they watch over and over, singing and dancing along with the movies.
